name: Happy Cake!
description:
This smiling little guy makes a great birthday gift. Or anytime gift. He is a cake with soft frosting and he is really glad to see you. Each piece is unique, with hand-embroidered faces. :)

Cotton and polyester. 
Measures approximately 6in. x 5 in. x 4 in.
This listing is for one piece of cake.

name: Hop Hop Bunny
description:
This bunny's face and "hop hop" are hand-printed from a hand-carved block by me using silk screen ink. Bunny has an unbleached, natural muslin front and is backed with lovely Denyse Schmidt fabric. 

Because of these qualities, each bunny rabbit is unique and the one you receive may differ slightly from the one actually pictured. The back each rabbit is differs due to the scale of the fabric.

Cotton and polyester filling.
Approx. 3 in. x 11 in. x 2 in.

name: Set of Clouds
description:
This set of three clouds comes with one happy cloud, one melancholy cloud, and one storm cloud. They are three little guys that you can hang near each other, or just hold. Very, very soft with hand-embroidery. 


Fleece, cotton, and polyester.
Approx. 8 in. x 5 in. x 3in.

name: Floresita apron
description:
Beautiful half-apron made from vintage fabric. A lovely bright green with a blue pocket, topped with a bow. Very cute and sassy.

Approx 19 in. x 23 in. with waist ties that measure 29 inches each from waistband to end. Approx. 77 inches across the top, including both ties.

Cotton/cotton blend.

name: Little Pink Apron
description:
Sexy little apron made from vintage fabric with a little blue bow and blue ties. 

Cotton.
Approx. 17 in. x 20 in. Measures 81 inches from the end of one tie to the other end.
